energy.usef.core.data.xml.bean.message

Class Prognosis

  • java.lang.Object
    • energy.usef.core.data.xml.bean.message.Prognosis
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Message

    public class Prognosis
extends Object
implements Message
    Prognosis messages are used to communicate A-plans and D-prognoses between USEF participants. Prognosis messages always contain a full list of PTUs for the Period they apply to, even if a Prognosis is sent after the start of the Period, when one or more PTUs are already in the operate or settlement phase. Receiving implementations should ignore the information supplied for those PTUs.
